high_descs: Turn around and walk to the microwave on the right side near the refrigerator.
Open the microwave and take out the egg on the left, then close the microwave.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the egg in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Put the egg in the refrigerator, in front of and to the right of the plastic dish, then close the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned egg in a refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn around and head towards the microwave to your right.
Take out the left egg inside the microwave.
Turn left to face the sink.
Place the egg in the right sink, wash it, and take it back out.
Turn around and head towards the fridge on your left.
Place the egg in front of the plate inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean egg from microwave into the fridge.
